headline: HALLA DIAMANTE QUE VALE MILES DE DÓLARES
author: NA
content: Surfers find a 'time capsule' and discover a diamond worth thousands of dollars.

headline: JAPONESES CELEBRAN DÍA DEL INODORO
author: NA
content: Today, November 10th, is the unofficial Day of the Toilet. The responsible party is the Japanese Toilet Association. The reason is that the numbers 11/10 can be read in Japanese as 'li-to ire' (good toilet).
